                            <comment id="12829815" author="civascu" created="Thu, 4 Feb 2010 22:07:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached proposed fix - the HConnectionManager.getHTableDescriptor(tableName) now calls MetaScanner.scan(&lt;b&gt;,&lt;/b&gt;,tableName).&lt;/p&gt;

